{"type": "article", "id": 48181, "title": "定制一副你居住城市的复古地图，做装饰画不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-12-12T23:10:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 46255, "name": "BoConcept"}, {"id": 22512, "name": "Good Thing"}, {"id": 46256, "name": "Mini Cloud Studios"}, {"id": 46257, "name": "Studio Steady"}, {"id": 46258, "name": "Christopher Specce"}, {"id": 22513, "name": "Jamie Wolfond"}, {"id": 46259, "name": "Hezin O"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 245, "image": "img/article/article_show/201712121745290snAlJBTDr2FRPpY.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>2018 Calendar by Hezin O</h3><p>韩国平面设计师 Hezin O 的新作是 2018 日历，灵感源自儿童学习用的字母卡片。整套日历由 12 张独立的卡片构成，每张卡片都有一个中央图示，月份的数字和单词首字母分别显示在左上角和右下角，日期环绕中心图示一圈。漫画一般的插图简单而有趣，创造出一种友好的充满童趣的美学形式，延续了 Hezin O 一贯以来的风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174600LQV3wCHX7xIYUBMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762431\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174600NSLlok9EwuCWRT1x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174600tmX6UdlMb9czYjQZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174600bVGjMIJcXQnCsEZ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174600ZHvt4ASCUBhaMi0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762431\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174600TkofNVY8QOA5vupF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762431\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/hezin-o-2018-calender-graphic-design-081217\" rel=\"nofollow\">It’s Nice That</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Shield Satchel by Studio Steady</h3><p>受到全球各地抗议活动频发的启发，跨学科设计团队 Studio Steady 为参与各种抗议维权活动的人士设计了一款护身包，拥有防水和防胡椒喷雾功能，采用抗冲击力极高的聚碳酸酯，内部厚厚的编织条带方便抓取，做成盾牌的样式。</p><p>Studio Steady 的首席设计师 Celine Setiadi 解释说，普通平民缺乏这一类装备，护身包的设计填补了这一市场空白，尽可能安全地帮助维权人士发表异议声音，因为他们既没有防暴盾牌，也没有警察自卫用的器具。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712121746316pdJs93AvRerobMT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174631n6OGydI2HDJ4ga1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.816626\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174631tJkXTHc9jzK7NQmq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712121746313uclLOUCYmHAxwKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.905868\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174632wFtXi0GDSsZoELYC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Modern Map Art Prints by Mini Cloud Studios</h3><p>许多人会在家中挂上复古的世界地图当装饰，来自伦敦的 Mini Cloud Studios 却认为，画出自己居住城市的空拍图更具意义，于是他们推出了订制服务，让人任意选取世界角落，填满喜爱的色调，将城市规划转化为艺术作品，色彩组合分为三个类别，柔和经典的 Retro-Vintage 系列，鲜艳明快的 Modern Bright 系列，以及偏灰调子的 Classic 系列。售价 14 至 41 英镑不等，<a href=\"https://map-art-prints.backerkit.com/hosted_preorders\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174713mMqOgpi7HexN5zLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174713KtNe02Gqj1VnUvpx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712121747139za0FyRGQJqO34et.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174713pavQoyksB0lL5Kjc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174713rNi7o1Yefd0Oph4g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174713437wrTevlIPsixhY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Platform Bowl by Jamie Wolfond</h3><p>Good Thing 是一个来自纽约布鲁克林的设计品牌，他们的产品大多线条简练，色彩充满暖意，比如这款名为 Platform 的碗，看上去更像是个长了脚的碟子，底座由松木构成，碗由粉末涂层钢材料制成，既可以单独使用，也可以组合起来堆叠使用，作为果盘、零食盘都是不错的选择，且会成为你餐桌上的吸睛好物。售价 32.5 美元，<a href=\"https://supergoodthing.com/collections/accessories/products/platform-bowl\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712121747427EJkzOq6l9581tRj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174742SOVlK8cZCoJN0Yda.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174742DvNMO0tfYHgxRziB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174742PHOeb0Nn2huWQ1m7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Richman Dustpan by Christopher Specce</h3><p>同样是一款来自 Good Thing 的产品 Richman Dustpan，设计师 Christopher Specce 对簸箕这种常见的日用器物进行了重新诠释，木制的毛刷工整地嵌入簸箕的手柄内，便于挂置收纳。Richman Dustpan 在形式和构造方面细腻而精致，不使用时，也可以是看起来不错的墙面装饰，至少不会是你在居家环境中想要刻意隐藏起来的物品。售价 29 美元，<a href=\"https://supergoodthing.com/collections/accessories/products/richman-dustpan\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174820EQ9arFbt4SiThfMA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174820iL1CjATdQSa82nuR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174820W1Sz4HhNRpyPY5A7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712121748212gxOGXdC4t5ArHEu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174821TQqdyogvEtpNuwx5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Milano Table by  BoConcept</h3><p>长方形的 Milano 餐桌，以利落的线条和流线型的外观呈现出美观，试图为任何餐厅制造时尚氛围。桌面的弧形收边，更添上几分柔和的味道。此外，坚实的中央底座，营造出大胆现代的外观，让这款餐桌成为引人注目的焦点。如果需要额外作为，只要拉出设计巧妙的内置延伸桌板，就能从四人家庭餐桌，变身成为 12 人座的晚宴桌。售价 39390 元，<a href=\"https://www.boconcept.com/zh-cn/milano/3700ACCT013CCEE.html?cgid=tables-diningtables\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174902R6zeFxvDyGq8iufp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174902YfTOGJE2nsbrhdPA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174902Sq9Y2GNvFU6QZsKm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666223\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174902XVwAHbPTvKyWlz0N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171212174902WCPajVgOtQMiUw3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}